      "docs": "CQRS command for the run-review-fix use case (sotp review fix-local). Carries stdlib-typed fields only (String, PathBuf — no domain / infrastructure types) per AC-01 and CN-01. Maps to the 7 CLI flags: --scope / --briefing-file / --track-id / --round-type / --reviewer-model / --model / --scope-files. round_type is a plain String (converted to ReviewRoundType internally by the interactor). The 7-flag shape mirrors the current Makefile.toml track-local-review-fix-codex bash arguments.",
